snippet.title: Kasparov's Gambit gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Kasparov's Gambit, Dos PC game produced by Electronic Arts in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/kasparov-s-gambit/5613/
Playing (and loosing) against Einstein opponent in this very beautiful chess simulation game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Beat the House - https://youtu.be/AhDMpCKt_x0
Ed Chess - https://youtu.be/D41pYzEXNwI
Mario's Game Gallery - https://youtu.be/Wk3PX-uYWCQ
